  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you damage a creature with an attack or a spell and the creature's size is larger than yours, you can cause the attack or spell to deal extra damage to the creature. The extra damage equals your proficiency bonus.</p><p>At 5th level, the extra damage equals twice your proficiency bonus.</p><p>You can use this trait a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, regaining all expended uses when you finish a long rest, and you can use it no more than once per turn.</p>",
